BT /F2 12 Tf 54 658.2 Td (Managing Your Guest List) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 630.4 Td (The guest list is often the most emotionally complex part of wedding planning. It affects) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 616.4 Td (your budget, venue size, catering costs, and overall atmosphere. Start with your ideal) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (number and work backward, making decisions as a team.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 578.6 Td (Tips for managing your guest list:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 564.6 Td (- Set a firm number early and stick to it) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 550.6 Td (- Divide invitations: 50% couple, 25% each family \(adjust as needed\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 536.6 Td (- Create an A-list \(must invite\) and B-list \(invite if space allows\)) Tj ET
